        {
            "id": 6021362,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 欣技(6160)大跌7.1%，報22.25元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6160:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6160\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6160-TW</a>)13日10:52股價下跌1.7元，報22.25元，跌幅7.1%，成交804張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6160:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6160\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6160-TW</a>)所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，主要業務為自動辨識掃描器及資料收集器製造買賣。電信管制射頻器材輸入及製造業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲0.21%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.32%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-15 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-78 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+63 張</li> <li>融資增減：+69 張</li> <li>融券增減：-6 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6021362",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-13 10:52:22",
